  {
    "number": 23,
    "title": "Erika Arendt, the Lone Girl",
    "overview": "Seated in the throne of the ruins of Nohal Naha, Erika's memories are awakened by the jewels. The plans for the nuclear fission device are projected and slowly drawn onto the parchment Kenshin gazes down upon...\n\nHearing Erika's heart-rending request to end her life, Kenshiro gently touches a pressure point on Erika's forehead.\n\nA single tear falls from Kenshiro's eyes.\n\n\"I'll protect the smile of the girl I see in front of me. That's a plenty good reason to fight.\"\n\nHis final battle as the 62nd successor to the Divine Fist of the North Star has finally begun.",
    "air_date": "2018-07-30",
    "still": "https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/psUr5G3uNUAgrXrHiZztwkhF2lU.jpg",
    "runtime": 26,
    "vote_average": 0,
    "tmdb_id": 1856797
  },
  {
    "number": 24,
    "title": "The Man Named Kasumi Kenshiro",
    "overview": "Kenshin's combined Heaven Dipper Sacred Yin Fist and Divine Fist of the North Star ultimate technique swallows up Kenshiro.\n\n\"This is the final blow... My history begins now!!\"\n\n\"Then I'll place the wishes of my pengyou in this blow...!!\"\n\nWhen two evenly-matched powerhouses battle one another, the Death Omen Star shines above both their heads. Destined by the North Star to kill one another, how will Kenshiro and Kenshin's battle end--?! Kenshiro's final battle is coming to a close!!",
    "air_date": "2018-07-31",
    "still": "https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/di1u0YJ7Jp1ryZ1qsGOp3r6M9Sq.jpg",
    "runtime": 26,
    "vote_average": 0,
    "tmdb_id": 1856798
